.DT
position
Discworld player help
position

.SH Name
.SI 5
position - Change or view your position
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
position [<new position>]
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Position lets you silently change your position, allowing you to
improve your health and well-being by experimenting with new and exciting
positions.  With no arguments, it will show your current position.  When
you change position, no message is sent to the room.

Each time you use this command, it will cost you 100 social points.
.EP

.SP 5 5
Please try to keep your positions inoffensive and in-theme with Discworld.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
sit, stand, lie, kneel, meditate, emote, crouch
.EP
